      <name>Dan_Wroblewski</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/72</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;This is my destination ... notice the URL is only the base endpoint.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736835371523.png" style="width: 824px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/211628i5A7150CFA77ACA40/image-dimensions/824x258?v=v2" width="824" height="258" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736835371523.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736835371523.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;These 4 videos shows you the entire process of triggering process from SAP Build Apps, from beginning to end. But if you are failing from Postman, then it would seem something else is wrong, since he destination is not involved there.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1208482666"&gt;Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #1 (free projects)&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;div class="video-embed-center video-embed"&gt;&lt;iframe class="embedly-embed" src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8RVo3-h2n-I%3Ffeature%3Doembed&amp;amp;display_name=YouTube&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8RVo3-h2n-I&amp;amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F8RVo3-h2n-I%2Fhqdefault.jpg&amp;amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;amp;schema=youtube" width="200" height="112" scrolling="no" title="Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #1 (free projects)" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1011969161"&gt;Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #2 - Retrieve Instances&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;div class="video-embed-center video-embed"&gt;&lt;iframe class="embedly-embed" src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F02dPZd1Btuw%3Ffeature%3Doembed&amp;amp;display_name=YouTube&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D02dPZd1Btuw&amp;amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F02dPZd1Btuw%2Fhqdefault.jpg&amp;amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;amp;schema=youtube" width="200" height="112" scrolling="no" title="Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #2 - Retrieve Instances" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-815455656"&gt;Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #3 - Retrieve Process Attributes&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;div class="video-embed-center video-embed"&gt;&lt;iframe class="embedly-embed" src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FPdlusgEMhiU%3Ffeature%3Doembed&amp;amp;display_name=YouTube&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPdlusgEMhiU&amp;amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FPdlusgEMhiU%2Fhqdefault.jpg&amp;amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;amp;schema=youtube" width="200" height="112" scrolling="no" title="Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #3 - Retrieve Process Attributes" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;DIV class=""&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-618942151"&gt;Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #4 - Cancel, Suspend, Resume Instances&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;div class="video-embed-center video-embed"&gt;&lt;iframe class="embedly-embed" src="https://cdn.embedly.com/widgets/media.html?src=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FJiVcTN0JIBU%3Ffeature%3Doembed&amp;amp;display_name=YouTube&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJiVcTN0JIBU&amp;amp;image=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FJiVcTN0JIBU%2Fhqdefault.jpg&amp;amp;type=text%2Fhtml&amp;amp;schema=youtube" width="200" height="112" scrolling="no" title="Trigger Process from SAP Build Apps #4 - Cancel, Suspend, Resume Instances" frameborder="0" allow="autoplay; fullscreen; encrypted-media; picture-in-picture;" allowfullscreen="true"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
