    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;ClientCredentials will work, but the metadata showing who started the process will be the Build Process Automation service itself; with JWTBearToken or UserTokenExchange you then know who triggered he process.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I do not see anything about adding the destination to the Control Tower in that documentation topic. Where did you see it?&lt;/P&gt;</content>
