    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/re-401-unauthorized-build-apps-unable-to-access-btp-de/qaq-p/13984975/comment-id/4898993#M4898993</id>
    <title>Re: 401 Unauthorized - Build Apps Unable to Access BTP De...</title>
    <updated>2025-01-14T10:22:35.529000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Dan_Wroblewski</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/72</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;IMPORTANT: I think what confused me is that you were connecting to SPA the "old way" and the documentation you referenced, though still valid, is somewhat superseded by the "new" way: &lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/build-apps/service-guide/processes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://help.sap.com/docs/build-apps/service-guide/processes&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;There are new flow functions that make connecting much easier and less error prone.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736846620502.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/211660i12F0BB44177AD624/image-size/medium?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736846620502.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1736846620502.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/re-401-unauthorized-build-apps-unable-to-access-btp-de/qaq-p/13984975/comment-id/4898993#M4898993"/>
    <published>2025-01-14T10:22:35.529000+01:00</published>
